						<summary>

						<p>This records a similar gift of one <hi rend="italic">kāśu</hi> for the (daily) supply of an earthen water pot to the temple by one Ādichchadēvi, the daughter of Śōḻanambi Kaḍambaṉ a resident of Śembanguḍi in Tiruvindaḷūr-nāḍu a subdivision of Rājādhirāja-vaḷanāḍu.</p>						

